'''Festimad''' is an [[alternative rock]] festival and cultural event held yearly in [[Madrid (autonomous community)|Madrid]], [[Spain]] since 1994, usually in the last week of May. Festimad includes several parallel cultural festivals such as Performa, Graffiti, Universimad o Cinemad, although its central event continues to be the music festival, standing alongside the [[Festival Internacional de Benicàssim]] as Spain's main rock concert.

